Saat bernama Kodam V/Brawijaya:

1. Korem 081/Dhirotsaha Jaya (DY)
2. Korem 082/Citra Panca Yudha Jaya (CPYJ)
3. Korem 083/Baladhika Jaya (BDJ)
4. Korem 084/Bhaskara Jaya (BJ)





